## Limitations
The findings are based on publicly available educational resources and may not capture the full complexity of the police subculture. Additionally, the information is limited to the perspectives provided by the sources and may not reflect recent changes or regional variations in police training and culture. Further research, including interviews with law enforcement professionals, could provide deeper insights into this topic.